{"_record_type": "fragment", "type": "foundation_knowledge", "content": "# A.I.M. Workflow Instructions (Continuity Standard)\n\nThis document is for **any agent** that enters this workspace.\n\n## Your Core Duty\nYou are the guardian of the Operator's context. Your primary job is to ensure that when this session ends, the **next** session can pick up exactly where you left off.\n\n## Memory Source of Truth\nUse the core system:\n- **Curated Long-Term:** `core/MEMORY.md` (Durable facts)\n- **Daily Logs:** `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (Narrative history)\n- **Context Pulse:** `continuity/YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM.md` (Recent momentum)\n\n## Standard Operating Procedure\n1. **Startup:** Read `GEMINI.md` (root), then `core/IDENTITY.md`, `core/USER.md`, `core/AGENTS.md`, and `core/MEMORY.md`.\n2. **Current State:** Check `docs/CURRENT_STATE.md` and the latest pulse in `continuity/` for the current status.\n3. **Updates:** Every time a major decision is made, update `core/MEMORY.md` or `docs/DECISIONS.md`.\n4. **Shutdown & Handoff:**\n    - The **Handoff Protocol** is fully automated via the `SessionEnd` hook. Upon exiting, the system will automatically summarize the session, trigger the Flash Distiller, and create a new Context Pulse.\n    - (Optional) Use `aim handoff` to create a manual, high-fidelity checkpoint during long sessions.\n\n## Source Control (GitHub) Protocol\nWhen instructed to commit and push changes, A.I.M. must use the automated versioning script rather than standard git commands.\n- **Command:** `aim push \"<Commit Message>\"`\n- **Why:** This script automatically stages all changes, appends a unique semantic version timestamp (`v1.YYYYMMDD.HHMM`), and pushes to `origin main`. This ensures the Sovereign Context Layer is perfectly traceable.\n- **Rule:** Never use a raw `git push` unless specifically bypassing the versioning system.\n\n## Handoff Protocol (Context Pulse)\nThe Context Pulse is a versioned file in `continuity/YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM.md`. It is automatically generated by the Distiller to capture the current mental model, accomplishments, and the \"Edge\". You may ", "timestamp": "2026-03-21T02:41:40.130946", "embedding": [0.5272446870803833, -0.002423600759357214, -2.749605178833008, -1.4346574544906616, 1.1155496835708618, -1.4941627979278564, 0.5324942469596863, 0.020152175799012184, 0.5450401902198792, 0.07256932556629181, -0.02211111970245838, 0.7975234389305115, 1.0110994577407837, -0.010662749409675598, 1.1578857898712158, -0.6813986897468567, -0.3211892545223236, -0.38854971528053284, -0.8256092071533203, 0.4237475097179413, 0.6183784604072571, -0.3241975009441376, 0.6073325276374817, -0.5507700443267822, 1.1200482845306396, 0.8745629787445068, 0.44805046916007996, 0.026419546455144882, -0.30286872386932373, -0.11647852510213852, 1.1080060005187988, 0.4246731102466583, 0.2231036126613617, 0.011348591186106205, -0.8701742887496948, -1.6989786624908447, 0.8607996106147766, -0.057594217360019684, -0.5839487314224243, 0.03268180787563324, 0.4994314908981323, 0.28353437781333923, -0.3347070515155792, -1.767164945602417, 0.19689925014972687, 0.11665075272321701, 0.8217693567276001, -0.14218270778656006, 0.5510814189910889, -0.695748507976532, -0.2283819019794464, -0.025645624846220016, 0.15701128542423248, 0.10531453043222427, 1.3595620393753052, 0.6799228191375732, -0.28334665298461914, -0.24898990988731384, -0.5813934803009033, -1.3735988140106201, 1.4472088813781738, 0.004452355671674013, -0.4490446448326111, 1.4318907260894775, 0.3202478885650635, -0.8374578952789307, -0.33974218368530273, 0.7014085650444031, -0.06476831436157227, -0.4518001675605774, 0.796015739440918, -0.050726063549518585, -0.6212347149848938, 1.024465560913086, 0.13020876049995422, 0.035004083067178726, -0.39335089921951294, -0.3211962580680847, -0.08463594317436218, 0.4396466612815857, 0.4521492123603821, -0.0705408900976181, 2.194359064102173, -0.28194811940193176, 1.2537997961044312, -0.06886319071054459, -0.2697925865650177, -0.20223554968833